location.fullValue: Prodigy Plan, Fairway at Stratford Place

data.description: Welcome to this recently built in 2022 stunning home located in Perris with NO HOA. Nestled on a spacious 0.33-acre lot, This gorgeous One-Story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms. With private Mountain views's situated on a corner lot. Many high-end upgrades includes wide plank hardwood floors through out, all 3 bathrooms are completely remodeled, a Brand New Heated POOL & Jacuzzi, etc. Featuring High 9-foot Ceilings, beautiful white kitchen cabinets, white Quartz  counter tops, Chef's kitchen with KitchenAid appliances. The master bedroom has a huge walk-in closet, a freestanding tub with separate shower. This home comes with PAID OFF SOLAR, Water conditioning system, fully Landscaped front and rear yard. A hard to find huge lot with over 14,000 SF flat lot, 3-car garage and Potential room for RV parking.  NO Neighbor behind.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this new home your home!! ...Hablo Espanol..-
